  <strong>This is the citizen-facing side of <a href="https://www.planx.uk/" class="govuk-link">PlanX</a>:</strong> Applicants answer plain English questions instead of filling in complex PDF forms. The system works out which planning permission is needed, what documents to collect, and whether the application can be submitted digitally. Councils using PlanX report that applicants find the process clearer and submit more complete applications first time.
